content: The Chill Elephants Club is a collection of 3,000 of the chillest algorithmically generated elephants on the Solana blockchain. We are a collection focused on bringing our community members value through exclusive airdrops, game play utility, and merchandise to elephant holders. One our main goals is to raise awareness for the fight against the ivory trade in Africa and help revitalize the African Elephant population by making a generous donation to Save the Elephants, a UK based charity, post launch.

One our main goals is to raise awareness for the fight against the ivory trade in Africa and help revitalize the African Elephant population by making a generous donation to Save the Elephants, a UK based charity, post launch.
